\mathcal{U}=-\int_{0}^{t}\mathcal{E}I\dd{t'}=-\int_{0}^{t}\frac{\dd{\Psi}}{\dd{t'}}I\dd{t'}=\int_{0}^{\Psi}I\dd{\Psi}.\label{eq:x6.1}
