f_{\alpha,1}=-\left(\int_{0}^{D}\sbf E\cdot\dd{\sbf D'}\right){\color{blue}\partial_{j}L_{\alpha}^{e}\,\det[J]}\dd{\hat{\Omega}}
\]

\end_inset

顺便改写积分测度：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sbf f_{\alpha,1}=-\left(\int_{0}^{D}\sbf E\cdot\dd{\sbf D'}\right)\nabla L_{\alpha}^{e}\,\dd{\Omega}
\]

