\begin_layout Itemize
这里的约定是，电位移矢量 
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf D=\alpha_{x}\frac{\partial\phi}{\partial x}\hat{x}+\alpha_{y}\frac{\partial\phi}{\partial y}\hat{y}+\alpha_{z}\frac{\partial\phi}{\partial z}\hat{z}$
